          "html": "<div class=\"code-block\">MODULE SortedSensorBuffer:\n    buffer = []  // sorted list of (sensor_id, timestamp, temperature)\n\n    FUNCTION ingest(reading):\n        pos = binary_search(buffer, reading.timestamp)\n        buffer.insert(pos, reading)\n        while buffer[0].timestamp &lt; current_time() - 60:\n            buffer.remove(0)\n\n    FUNCTION poll():\n        return copy(buffer)</div>\n<p class=\"text-sm\" style=\"margin-top:8px\"><strong>Vergleichstabelle:</strong></p>\n<table class=\"comparison-table\"><thead><tr><th>Kriterium</th><th>Einfügesortierung (gewählt)</th><th>Mergesort</th><th>Quicksort</th></tr></thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr><td>Zeit (pro Element)</td><td>O(log n) Suche + O(n) Verschiebung</td><td>O(n log n) vollständige Neusortierung</td><td>O(n log n) vollständige Neusortierung</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Speicher</td><td>O(1) zusätzlich</td><td>O(n)</td><td>O(log n) Stapel</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Latenz</td><td>Niedrig pro Element</td><td>Hohe Batch-Latenz</td><td>Hohe Batch-Latenz</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n",
